ily: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Premium rate per palm ranges from Rs. 9.00 (in the plant age group of 4 to 15 years) to Rs. 14.00 (in the plant age group of 16-60 years).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 100%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 100%; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;50-75% subsidy of premium is provided to all types of farmers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 6.7pt 0.0001pt 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 100%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 100%; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;When the palm damaged, the claim payment equal to input cost loss damage is payable to the insured in notified areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 241.55pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 24.15pt; background: #DDDDDD; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0.1pt 0cm 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11.5pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 6.45pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 140.7pt; background: #DDDDDD; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0.1pt 0cm 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11.5pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;m